Name: Stewart The Fox
About the game: Welcome to Stewart the Fox!⠀ in this action-packed platformer, you'll play as Stewart, a brave fox on a quest to defeat enemies, overcome obstacles, and emerge victorious.⠀ As you journey through the game's four levels, you'll encounter a variety of challenges and foes, including tricky jumps, dangerous enemies and two epic boss battles. With quick reflexes and clever strategy, you'll need to navigate through each level and emerge unscathed. But the challenges don't stop there! Throughout the game, you'll also be on the lookout for collectibles hidden throughout the levels. So grab your controller / mouse and join Stewart on his epic adventure. Can you help him emerge victorious and claim victory in Stewart the Fox? NOTE: This game is meant to be challenging depending on your Platformer skills. NOTE: Controllers are supported in-game, not in Menu's. NOTE: This game is made by a single developer in the timespan of 2 weeks. Stewart The Fox Game Art:
